OL,5, The New Zealand-based visual effects   
OL,6, studio co-founded by Oscar-winning     
OL,7, director Sir Peter Jackson has been    
OL,8, sold for $1.6bn (_1.2bn).              
OL,10,FWeta Digital, which has worked on films
OL,11,Fincluding Lord of the Rings and Avatar,
OL,12,Fis being bought by video games software
OL,13,Fcompany Unity.                         
OL,15,FUnity's technology is behind games such
OL,16,Fas Pokemon Go and Call of Duty: Mobile.
OL,18,FThe firms say the deal means that      
OL,19,FWeta's special effects tools will be   
OL,20,F"democratised".                        
